DTEND:20190205T182500Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Benefits fueled by the modularity of the pulp plugin ecosystem by taking the example of pulp_deb and pulp_gem.</p>

<p>Pulp is a rest-api driven, plugin based framework for content repository management.<br />
Despite being used unmediated, it is also employed as a key backend component in foreman/katello.<br />
